  "texts": [
    "In all benchmarks, our models exceed the performance of the officially instruct models, which rely on closed-source datasets and algorithms.",
    "We believe our easily reproducible study offers useful insights for alignment research, and our fine-tuned models are valuable for downstream applications.",
    "Our contributions are:",
    "• We present a rigorous analysis of modern alignment training pipelines, and identify a set of design choices that significantly impact the performance of language models.",
    "• We aggregate our empirical findings into a step-by-step recipe, and show that our models outperform the officially released instruct models, which relies on closed-source datasets and algorithms."
